name: Autody
description: Autody Inc. (AU) is a publicly traded technology hardware company focused on innovation in microprocessors, smart devices, and AI-powered solutions. Known for products like the AutodyChip and AutodyVR, the company is driving progress in consumer electronics, industrial tech, and healthcare wearables. With a market cap of $69.35 million, Autody is emerging as a leader in next-gen hardware and is now open to investors through its IPO.
